[BINARY MODEL PLACEHOLDER]

This file location is reserved for the compiled machine learning pipeline trained on the Everglades Agricultural Area (EAA) Histosol library.

To protect intellectual property prior to the formal publication of this PhD research, the actual serialized model weights, preprocessing scalars, and coefficients have been omitted from this public repository. 

The fully calibrated, operational .joblib file will be released and synced to this repository alongside the peer-reviewed paper.
